The '''2019 [[Games of the Small States of Europe]]''', also known as the '''XVIII Games of the Small States of Europe''', that will take place in 2019 in [[Budva]],<ref>{{cite web|title=Budva će biti domaćin Igara malih zemalja|trans-title=Budva will be the host of the games of small states|url=http://www.rtcg.me/sport/ostali-sportovi/126318/budva-ce-biti-domacin-igara-malih-zemalja-.html|website=rtcg.me|publisher=[[RTCG]]|accessdate=27 January 2017|language=Montenegrin|date=21 April 2016}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|last1=Lajović|first1=Vuk|title=Budva će 2019. biti domaćin Igara malih država Evrope|trans-title=Budva will be the host of the 2019 Games of the Small States of Europe|url=http://www.vijesti.me/sport/budva-ce-2019-biti-domacin-igara-malih-drzava-evrope-884693?piano_t=1|website=vijesti.me|publisher=Vijesti|accessdate=27 January 2017|language=Montenegrin|date=21 April 2016}}</ref> [[Montenegro]], from 27 May to 1 June 2019.<ref>http://www.montenegro2019.me</ref><ref>https://allsportdb.com/Games/2019-Games-of-the-Small-States-of-Europe-82</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.timesofmalta.com/articles/view/20150602/sport/montenegro-to-host-2019-edition.570704|title=Montenegro to host 2019 edition|last=Camilleri|first=Valhmor|date=June 2, 2015|work=[[Times of Malta]]|access-date=2017-05-16|archive-url=|archive-date=|dead-url=|language=en-GB}}</ref>

