{{Infobox National handball team | country= Belgium | name= | type= M | Badge= Flag of Belgium.svg | Nickname=''The Red Wolves'' | Association= [[Royal Belgian Handball Federation]] (URBH) | Coach= | Captain= | Most caps= | Most goals= <!-- Home colours --> | pattern_la1=|pattern_b1=_Angola|pattern_ra1= | leftarm1=FF0000|body1=FF0000|rightarm1=FF0000|shorts1=000000|socks1=FF0000 <!-- Away colours --> | pattern_la2=|pattern_b2=_Angola|pattern_ra2= | leftarm2=FFFFFF|body2=FFFFFF|rightarm2=FFFFFF|shorts2=FFFFFF|socks2=FFFFFF <!-- Results --> | Summer Olympics apps = 0 | World cup apps = 0 | Regional cup apps = 0 | updated = 16 November 2017 }}
The '''Belgium national handball team''' is the national team of [[Belgium]]. It is governed by the [[Royal Belgian Handball Federation]] and takes part in international [[team handball|handball]] competitions. As of 2017, it never participated in major international tournaments.
