{{Infobox football club | clubname = Blue Boys| image = | fullname = Blue Boys | nickname = | founded = 1958 | ground = [[Vineta Central Sport Grounds]], [[Swakopmund]] | capacity = 2000 | chairman = {{flagicon|Namibia}} Peter Ngobeni| manager = {{flagicon|Namibia}} ?| league = [[Namibia Premier League]] | season = | position = | }}
'''Blue Boys''' is a [[Namibia]]n [[football (soccer)]] club from [[Swakopmund]]. They play in the country's highest division, the [[Namibia Premier League]].
The team was founded in 1958.
==Stadium== Currently the team plays at the 2000 capacity [[Vineta Central Sport Grounds]].
