{{Cleanup|reason=Page is incomplete|date=October 2015}} {{Infobox Athletic Conference |name = Chushikoku Collegiate American Football Association |short_name = 中四国学生アメリカンフットボール連盟 |established = |logo = |logo_size = 500 |association = |division = |subdivision = |members = |sports = |mens = |womens = |region = [[Shikoku]]/[[Chūgoku region|Chūgoku]] |former_names = |hq_city = |hq_state = |commissioner = |since = |website = {{URL|http://www.cscaa.jp/}} |color = #0088CE |font_color = white |map = |map_size = }}
The '''Chushikoku Collegiate American Football Association (中四国学生アメリカンフットボール連盟)''' is an [[American football|American]] [[college football]] league made up of colleges and universities primarily on the island of [[Shikoku]]; two schools are located in the [[Chūgoku region]] of [[Honshū]].
