The '''Pakistan national under-17 football team''' is the under-17 football (soccer) team of [[Pakistan]]. The team has participated in the [[AFC U-16 Championship]] once in [[2002 AFC U-17 Championship|2002]] and has also participated in the [[SAFF U-16 Championship]] in [[2011 SAFF U-16 Championship|2011]] and [[2013 SAFF U-16 Championship|2013]], but withdrew in [[2015 SAFF U-16 Championship|2015]] and did not enter in [[2017 SAFF U-15 Championship|2017]].

