'''Sidi Mohamed Ould Bidjel''' (born 1 January 1982), is a [[Mauritania]]n athlete.

Bidjel competed in the [[Athletics at the 2000 Summer Olympics – Men's 1500 metres|1500 metres]] at the [[2000 Summer Olympics]], he finished 14th in his heat so didn't qualify for the next round.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.sports-reference.com/olympics/athletes/ou/sidi-mohamed-ould-bidjel-1.html|title=Sidi Mohamed Ould Bidjel Bio, Stats, and Results|website=Olympics at Sports-Reference.com|language=en|access-date=2018-05-14}}</ref>

