It is currently used mostly for [[rugby union]] matches and is the home stadium of [[Stade Montois]], [[2012–13 Top 14 season|currently]] playing in [[Rugby union in France|the country's]] top league, the [[Top 14]].<ref>[http://www.worldstadiums.com/europe/countries/france/aquitaine.shtml World Stadiums - Stadiums in France :: Aquitaine<!-- Bot generated title -->]</ref> The stadium can hold 22,000 people and opened in 1965.
